OL,3,CWhose responsibility is pollution in
OL,4,CUK seas, and how is it cleaned up?
OL,6,FOn Monday morning, a tanker carrying
OL,7,Fjet fuel collided with a cargo ship
OL,8,Foff the coast of East Yorkshire,
OL,9,Fsparking a fire onboard, and
OL,10,Fenvironmental concerns for the North
OL,11,FSea.
OL,13,FThe company running the tanker, the
OL,14,FStena Immaculate, confirmed that a
OL,15,Ftank containing Jet-A1 fuel was
OL,16,Fruptured during the collision, with
OL,17,Ffuel released into the water as a
OL,18,Fresult.
