OL,3,CWhose responsibility is pollution in
OL,4,CUK seas, and how is it cleaned up?
OL,6,FBut what happens when pollution is
OL,7,Freleased into UK seas, and whose job
OL,8,Fis it to clean it up? ITV News
OL,9,Fexplains.
OL,11,FHow is pollution defined when it comes
OL,12,Fto our seas?
OL,14,FPollution in the seas and oceans is
OL,15,Fdefined as "any substance that could
OL,16,Fbe damaging to the marine environment."
