OL,3,CWhose responsibility is pollution in
OL,4,CUK seas, and how is it cleaned up?
OL,6,FWhich organisation takes the lead
OL,7,Fdepends exactly on the situation.
OL,8,FPublic agencies will often work
OL,9,Ftogether to respond to incidents at
OL,10,Fsea.
OL,12,FA local port or harbour authority will
OL,13,Fhave a duty to respond within areas
OL,14,Fthey control. They usually have their
OL,15,Fown counter pollution equipment to
OL,16,Fdeploy.
