OL,3,CWhose responsibility is pollution in
OL,4,CUK seas, and how is it cleaned up?
OL,6,FCommercial companies also have a legal
OL,7,Fobligation to act if they cause
OL,8,Fpollution, with their responses
OL,9,Fclosely scrutinised and monitored by
OL,10,Fthe Coastguard. The Counter Pollution
OL,11,Fand Salvage Team, a part of HM
OL,12,FCoastguard, will swing into action
OL,13,Fwhen there is a serious risk of
OL,14,Fpollution at sea, and where a rapid
OL,15,Fresponse is required.
OL,17,FHow do teams react to pollution?
