OL,4,CUK seas, and how is it cleaned up?
OL,6,FTo achieve this containment, the
OL,7,FCoastguard has a toolkit at its
OL,8,Fdisposal:
OL,10,FHow can pollution be stopped from
OL,11,Fhappening?
OL,13,FEnsuring the safety and seaworthiness
OL,14,Fof vessels is essential to avoiding
OL,15,Fthe kinds of incidents that lead to
OL,16,Fmajor pollution.
OL,18,FHM Coastguard is part of the Maritime
OL,19,Fand Coastguard Agency, which has
OL,20,Fhundreds of people working every day
OL,21,Fto keep the waters around the UK safe.
