OL,3,CWhose responsibility is pollution in
OL,4,CUK seas, and how is it cleaned up?
OL,6,FSurveyors for the Maritime and
OL,7,Fcoastguard Agency regularly check an
OL,8,Farray of vessels, from water taxis to
OL,9,Foil tankers, which operate on UK
OL,10,Fcoasts to ensure they are in proper
OL,11,Fcondition to sail safely and cleanly.
